Darren: I use propane. I slipped a piece of tygon tubing onto the 
snout of my propane cylinder and terminated the other end with a 12" 
piece of aluminum tubing. The tubing is just a convenient stiff 
handle/nozzle  to direct the gas at various places on the manifold.
